THE LIST OF DCECP OBJECT REF PAGE CHANGES:
******************************************
The following list of dcecp changes was taken from section 1.1 of:

   457385 Sep  8 13:17 /users/melman/dsh/doc/rfc42.3.txt

Generally these items identify changes that must be incorporated into
the dcecp object reference pages.   My comments are flush left. 
**************************


       (bm) Added `registry verify'.

       (bn) Added `-randompwd' option to `account modify'.

See item (dc) which removes the `-ramdompwd' option.

       (bo) Removed ERA's from the `registry' object.

       (bp) Changed `-c' option to `dcecp' to take one value instead of the
            rest of the arguments.  This is so adding more options to
